XSbm0/RxMvObpI17sv/EDTGrGZkA==\",\n./package-lock.json:4162:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-f7rPLi/T1HVKZu/u6t87lroib16n8vrSzcyxI7lg4BGO9UF26KhQL44sd9eOUgrTYhvRXtWOIZT5PejdPyJfUA==\",\n./package-lock.json:7416:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-RKtWF8pGmS87i2D6gqQu/l7EYRlVdfzemCJN/P3UOs//x1QE7mfhvzHIApBTRf7axvT6DMGwSwBXYCT0nfB9xw==\",\n./package-lock.json:7972:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-Bdboy+l7tA3OGW6FjyFHWkP5LuByj1Tk33Ljyq0axyzdk9//JSi2u3fP1QSmd1KNwq6VOKYGlAu87CisVir6Pw==\",\n./package-lock.json:9533:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-oj87CgZICdulUohogVAR7AjlC0327U4el4L6eAvOqCeudMDVU0NThNaV+b9Df4dXgSP1gXMTnPdhfe/2qDH5cg==\",\n./package-lock.json:9938:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-VXJjc87FScF88uafS3JllDgvAm+c/Slfz06lorj2uAY34rlUu0Nt+v8wreiImcrgAjjIHp1rXpTDlLOGw29WwQ==\",\n./package-lock.json:10494:      \"integrity\": \"sha512-UhDfHmA92YAlNnCfhmq0VeNL5bDbiZGg7sZ2IvPsXubGkiNa9EC+tUTsjBRsYUAz87btI6/1wf4XoVvQ3uRnmQ==\",\n./automation/tasks.json:8:    \"prompt\": \"Perform a preflight audit only. Do not edit files. Inspect package.json, app route tree, app/page.tsx, components/LandingPage.tsx, components/Header.tsx, components/Footer.tsx, components/sections, lib/site-map-data.ts, lib/public-page-content.ts, lib/landing-data.ts, lib/blueprint-data.ts, lib/frontend-placeholders.ts, components/Phase2PublicPages.tsx, components/Phase2InteractivePanels.tsx, and components/CommandCenter.tsx if they exist. Confirm the framework, routing model, styling stack, animation libraries, current page architecture, and whether framer-motion or motion/react is installed. Confirm whether any Aceternity UI components already exist; do not install anything. Check that there is no app/[...slug]/page.tsx and no components/PublicRoutePage.tsx. Search for PublicRoutePage imports and slug catch-all references. Check whether the landing page has all required homepage sections: Hero, Enterprise Quick Search, Garage Foundry Factory journey, What We Build, Interactive Experience, Global Presence, Client Success, Live Dashboard, Latest Research, Contact, Footer. Check whether all public pages are explicit App Router pages. Check whether the Blueprint scoring formula exists and whether the banking test case can return 87/100. Produce a gap list only. Do not edit files. Final response must include files inspected, missing items, route gaps, homepage gaps, design-system observations, animation-library availability, and recommended next task.\"\n./automation/tasks.json:104:    \"prompt\": \"Verify and fix the Blueprint Generator. It must be frontend-only and may appear on homepage and /build/blueprint. It must include title: Get Your Enterprise AI Blueprint in 60 Seconds. Required inputs: Industry, Company Size, Top Priorities with max 3 selection, AI Journey, Data Readiness, Leadership Commitment, Biggest Challenge, Email, OTP placeholder. Optional: Budget and Geography. It must not send real OTP or call backend. Formula: Blueprint Score = 0.20(AI Maturity)+0.25(Business Need)+0.20(Data Readiness)+0.20(Process Complexity)+0.15(Transformation Readiness). Scoring: No AI 10, Exploring AI 30, Running Pilots 60, Scaling AI 85, AI-Driven Enterprise or AI-Native 100. Business Need: Cost Reduction 20, Productivity 20, Customer Experience 15, Revenue Growth 15, Compliance 10, AI Transformation 20, Automate Processes 20, capped at 100. Data Readiness: Highly fragmented 20, Partially connected 50, Mostly integrated 75, Fully integrated 100. Process Complexity: <100 20, 100-1000 50, 1000-10000 80, 10000+ 100. Transformation Readiness: Not Discussed 20, Exploring 50, Budget Approved 80, Executive Mandate 100. Categories: 0-25 AI Beginner, 26-50 AI Explorer, 51-70 AI Adopter, 71-85 AI Transformer, 86-100 AI-Native Leader. Test example Banking, 15000 employees, Scaling AI, Productivity + Cost Reduction + Compliance, Mostly Integrated Data, Budget Approved must display 87/100. Required outputs: AI Readiness Score, Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunities, Recommended GFF AI Solution, Expected Business Impact, 90-Day Roadmap. Label impacts as expected/modelled, not guaranteed. Run lint/build.\"\n./automation/tasks.json:304:    \"prompt\": \"Perform final QA for the complete Phase 0 to Phase 2 build. Do not add new features unless fixing a small clear issue. Verify landing page has approved hero preserved, hero video placement unchanged, hero copy and metrics correct, Enterprise Quick Search present and local, Garage Foundry Factory journey present, What We Build present, Interactive Experience present, Global Presence present, Client Success present, Live Dashboard present without fake numbers, Latest Research present, Footer complete. Verify explicit routes exist and no slug logic or PublicRoutePage exists. Verify all public pages have premium unique UI, category design families, mobile responsiveness, accessibility basics, no fake data, no backend/API/AWS/auth/OTP/export behavior. Verify Blueprint banking test returns 87/100. Run npm run lint and npm run build if available. Final response must include pass/fail checklist, files changed in final QA, commands run, remaining warnings, and any remaining TODOs.\"\nBinary file ./.git/objects/66/2d91bada3f1b38a1c070f507a052aa8e1bf7a1 matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/50/6509286473e1cfa44bab2c89664153eb95ebad matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/9b/b8a0c59825fc992d21ebadcbd18c0d8d92ca3c matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/0e/af486ee440f88ffff43676910cf101210aaae5 matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/33/ce962f758e7d714ec741e388b34d38d11da5a7 matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/a3/f77598761d3f77329165742049d9a201a4d7a5 matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/bd/6cbf8044d9a81192b79702be991b0e483dfd73 matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/c0/3da350ae3bd713fa47669040d7b223d4c5d16e matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/27/62289dfab2944d9c1766179288f8678998f5ec matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/pack/pack-813fa146cd0310ab4b3e802ce8b36d832d6e0ad3.pack matches\nBinary file ./.git/objects/16/c670b1bffe7fe557fce5d7d57527f622c72