ore` function is receiving hardcoded values, resulting in a static score of 64. My \"Banking\" test case demands an 87/100, which confirms the gap. The generator needs to dynamically map user inputs to maturity scores. I now see my next task is to verify and fix the blueprint generator scoring mechanism, or to perform a final safety cleanup step.\n\n\n"}}
